on Atkins MacNeil]]\n|1935\n|Vermont marble\n|\n|-\n|}\n\n===Pedimental sculptures (by state, city & building)===\n\n==Alabama==\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! width=\"10%\" | Building\n! width=\"10%\" | Location\n! width=\"5%\" | Image\n! width=\"15%\" | Sculpture\n! width=\"10%\" | Sculptor\n! width=\"10%\" | Architect\n! width=\"5%\" | Installed\n! width=\"10%\" | Medium\n! width=\"25%\" | Notes\n|-\n|[[Calhoun County Courthouse (Alabama)|Calhoun County Courthouse]]\n|25 West 11th Street,<br>[[Anniston, Alabama|Anniston]]\n|[[File:Calhoun County, Alabama Courthouse.JPG|100px]]\n|Eagle pediment\n|\n|[[J. W. Golucke]]\n|1900<br>burned 1931\n|\n|a flying eagle flanked by [[fasces]] and [[cornacopia]]s\n|-\n|}\n\n==Arizona==\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! width=\"10%\" | Building\n! width=\"10%\" | Location\n! width=\"5%\" | Image\n! width=\"15%\" | Sculpture\n! width=\"10%\" | Sculptor\n! width=\"10%\" | Architect\n! width=\"5%\" | Installed\n! width=\"10%\" | Medium\n! width=\"25%\" | Notes\n|-\n|[[Santa Cruz County Courthouse (Nogales, Arizona)|Santa Cruz County Courthouse]]<ref>[http://siris-artinventories.si.edu/ipac20/ipac.jsp?session=14T8G92523375.114&menu=search&aspect=Keyword&npp=50&ipp=20&spp=20&profile=ariall&ri=&term=&index=.GW&aspect=Keyword&term=&index=.AW&term=&index=.TW&term=&index=.SW&term=&index=.FW&term=&index=.OW&term=AZ000452&index=.NW&x=11&y=9 Santa Cruz County Courthouse], from SIRIS.</ref>\n|Morley Avenue & Court Street,<br>[[Nogales, Arizona|Nogales]]\n|[[File:Santa_Cruz_Court_House_pediment.jpg|100px]]\n|\n|\n|[[Trost & Trost|Trost & Rust]]\n|1904\n|\n|[[File:Santa Cruz County Courthouse.jpg|100px|right]]Now a museum.\n|-\n|}\n\n==California==\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! width=\"10%\" | Building\n! width=\"10%\" | Location\n! width=\"5%\" | Image\n! width=\"15%\" | Sculpture\n! width=\"10%\" | Sculptor\n! width=\"10%\" | Architect\n! width=\"5%\" | Installed\n! width=\"10%\" | Medium\n! width=\"25%\" | Notes\n|-\n|